    <p>{`For more information and a great overview of what the Jamstack is and some more of its benefits i recommend checking out
`}<a parentName="p" {...{
        "href": "https://jamstack.org/"
      }}>{`jamstack.org`}</a>{`.`}</p>
    <p>{`Just because our site is served as static assets, that doesn't mean we cant work in a dynamic way and have the benefits
