    <p>{`Fauna also provides us with a High Availability solution with each server globally located containing a partition of our
database, replicating our data asynchronously with each request with a copy of our database or the transaction made.`}</p>
    <p>{`Some of the benefits to using Fauna can be summarized as:`}</p>
